    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>creamy pie filling</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> and top with the <strong>mash</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until bubbling and golden – this is your <strong>creamy veg-packed potato-topped pie</strong></p><p>Tip: Use individual oven dishes for fancy presentation!</p><p>Once the pie is almost done, heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>over a medium heat</p>",
